==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
Combination of ''[[elevator]]'' and Latin ''[[scala]]'' meaning "steps"

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[moving]] [[staircase]]; a device consisting of [[revolve|revolving]] [[stair]]s that conveys people non-vertically to a higher or lower level.

